    {
        "sha": "56f9a5dd242e73224beada91c93a60ce65936a75",
        "author": "sakno",
        "email": "roman.sakno@gmail.com",
        "date": "2026-07-11T18:54:14Z",
        "message": "Avoid touching cancellation/timer state while activation is in flight\n\nActivation and completion are allowed to race by design (activation can\nnever start once completion has begun, but completion can begin while\nactivation is still running). If a completion wins that race, resetting\ntokenTracker/timeoutTracker from the completing thread could collide with\nActivate() still writing them on the other thread.\n\nAdd IsActivating and gate the reset in NotifyConsumer/EndCompletion: when\nactivation is still in progress, skip the reset via DoNotResetOptions and\ndefer it to the next Reset() call, which already spins until activation\nhas fully finished before touching the same state itself.",
        "url": "https://github.com/dotnet/dotNext/commit/56f9a5dd242e73224beada91c93a60ce65936a75"
    },
